			&laquo; <a href="http://samablog.robsama.com/?p=4806" rel="prev">The Results Of Obama&#8217;s Speech Are In</a> &bull; <a href="http://samablog.robsama.com/?p=4823" rel="next">Storm Truthers</a> &raquo;		</div>

